room_title: Escape room "Professor Moriarty’s Gameroom" by The Great Escape Room in Akron
review: Came here on New Year’s Day, and halfway through, my boyfriend proposed with a blacklight-revealed “clue”! Most amazing idea I could have ever imagined and Kasey was wonderful for making the clue and making it all run smoothly. Best of all, we escaped!!

room_title: Escape room "Professor Moriarty’s Gameroom" by The Great Escape Room in Akron
review: Had a great time! The "Game Room" was super hard, but really fun! Megan was wonderful! Great escape room!

room_title: Escape room "Professor Moriarty’s Gameroom" by The Great Escape Room in Akron
review: Fun, fun, fun! Professor Moriarty's Game was challenging and enjoyable.
